title: Vite
altText: Vite is a local development server written by Evan You and used by default by the Vue project templates. It has support for TypeScript and JSX.

title: GitHub
altText: GitHub, Inc. is an Internet hosting service for software development and version control using Git. It provides the distributed version control of Git plus access control, bug tracking, software feature requests, task management, continuous integration, and wikis for every project
